abstract: “There is in fact overwhelming evidence that the president withheld the military aid directly to get a personal political benefit,” Jason Crow of Colorado, one of the managers, said.
lead_paragraph: House managers used a question from Senator Dianne Feinstein, Democrat of California, to reiterate the heart of their case: accusing President Trump’s lawyers of incorrectly stating that there is no evidence that Mr. Trump linked security assistance to investigations.
